description:
Eva and Richelle have been in this situation before… They just don’t Remember it! They Find a pair of Headphones, put them on, transform into robots and now they are deep under the Master’s control.

There’s nothing this two won’t do when they remain in the Headphones sway! The best part… They won’t remember anything afterwards!
title: HEADPHONES OF ROBOTIC DESTINY 2: The Return of Absolute Control
